description:
2 - Israel in Prophecy: Israel and Jesus Christ - Part 2 of "Israel In Prophecy", a 5-part TV series with bestselling author and speaker Steve Wohlberg. In this presentation you will discover the New Testament distinction between "Israel after the flesh" (1 Corinthians 10:18)  and the "Israel of God" (Galatians 6:14-16) centered in Jesus Christ. You will also gain vital insights into what the book of Revelation really says about Mount Zion, the New Jerusalem, the Heavenly Temple, Babylon the Great and Armageddon. This timely resource has been a blessing to thousands around the world, and will prove to be a blessing to you!

For more resources and to order the entire "Israel in Prophecy" series on DVD, visit http://www.whitehorsemedia.com.
